Great joy in camp we are in View of the Ocian,
                   [NB: in the morning when fog cleared off just below last village just on leaving the village of Warkiacum
                  ], this great Pacific Octean which we been So long anxious to See. and the roreing or noise made by the waves brakeing on the rockey Shores (as I Suppose) may be heard distictly
